EN: I like to eat stir-fried vegetables.

ZH: 请你帮我买些新鲜的蔬菜。
EN: Please help me buy some fresh vegetables.

ZH: 蔬菜对身体健康非常有好处。
EN: Vegetables are very good for your health.

